== Globalize3 Rails Example app

To get started

<tt>
git clone git://github.com/tinderfields/globalize3_example.git
cd globalize3_example
rake db:create
rake db:schema:load
rails server
</tt>

Visit http://0.0.0.0:3000/pages and create a page. 

If you then switch locale you can add other translations

View the commits at https://github.com/tinderfields/globalize3_example/commits/master to see what I've added from the default install

